g","release_date":"","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Pain","original_language":"en"},{"id":33135,"adult":false,"title":"Fun","video":false,"overview":"Hillary and Bonnie meet one morning by the side of the road. They become fast friends, share their secrets, and, on a rising wave of frenzy, later that afternoon, murder an old woman. They did it, they say later, for fun.","genre_ids":[18,53,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.295,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/vXsCYOI6v3baMTzLlMho78FO6Hn.jpg","release_date":"1994-10-12","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/ckhW4ZAnxKY4nEhoPo9lOsyR6be.jpg","original_title":"Fun","original_language":"en"},{"id":1215589,"adult":false,"title":"FILM","video":false,"overview":"A man tries to make a film but gets sick.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.07,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/gqdtIZDemygfGUcYI1SxLxXLDtz.jpg","release_date":"2019-06-19","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/od7xeqFKe3gKDSVoOEJz6lAfzpf.jpg","original_title":"FILM","original_language":"fr"},{"id":366363,"adult":false,"title":"CodeGirl","video":false,"overview":"Join high school-aged girls from around the world as they try to better their community through technology and collaboration in this thrilling, heartfelt documentary.  By 2017, the app market will be valued at $77 Billion. Over 80% of these developers are male. The Technovation Challenge aims to change that by empowering girls worldwide to develop apps for an international competition. From rural Moldova to urban Brazil to suburban Massachusetts, CODEGIRL follows teams who dream of holding their own in the world’s fastest-growing industry. The winning team gets $10K to complete and release their app, but every girl discovers something valuable along the way.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4057,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/imzycsyg93D0tXLs1BEcy2BsIDz.jpg","release_date":"2015-11-01","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":null,"original