 and Robby are a married couple having a hard time connecting with each other as the holidays approach. Just before Christmas, they head to a cozy Vermont inn at the advice of their marriage coach so they can recharge. Their weekend away gets unexpectedly extended when a mishap puts their car out of commission and just may put them on the road to a very happily married Christmas.","genre_ids":[10770,35,10749],"popularity":0.3163,"vote_count":36,"poster_path":"/cZjDTEpZ0SPER7NuuIIjPlGwEP8.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-22","vote_average":5.167,"backdrop_path":"/94hfGX8TSFJdgN0Upq3xnQVAoNW.jpg","original_title":"We Wish You a Married Christmas","original_language":"en"},{"id":796438,"adult":false,"title":"A Tiny House Christmas","video":false,"overview":"A restless young woman finds herself working a seasonal job as an elf - and moving into a tiny house fit for one. When she unwraps a coworker's greatest secret, she must come up with a plan as big as Christmas.","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":0.0697,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/EQNOK6tdG98H1aZI0fOcXjut5g.jpg","release_date":"2021-02-12","vote_average":3.4,"backdrop_path":"/47bEom95WA3xT3KhJcZVgY1yDw4.jpg","original_title":"A Tiny House Christmas","original_language":"en"},{"id":103,"adult":false,"title":"Taxi Driver","video":false,"overview":"Suffering from insomnia, disturbed loner Travis Bickle takes a job as a New York City cabbie, haunting the streets nightly, growing increasingly detached from reality as he dreams of cleaning up the filthy city.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":13.4122,"vote_count":13213,"poster_path":"/ekstpH614fwDX8DUln1a2Opz0N8.jpg","release_date":"1976-02-09","vote_average":8.127,"backdrop_path":"/9uddYYTNcLWpzUkl5iw1RUYhLhY.jpg","original_title":"Taxi Driver","original_language":"en"},{"id":185,"adult":false,"title":"A Clockwork Orange","video":false,"overview":"In a near-future Britain, young Alexander DeLarge and his pals get their kicks beating and raping anyone they please. When not destroying the lives of others, Alex swoons to the music of Beethoven. The state, eager to crack down on juvenile crime, gives an incarcerated Alex the option to undergo an invasive procedure that'll rob him of all personal agency. In a time when conscience is a commodity, can Alex change his tune?","genre_ids":[878,80],"popularity":10.4038,"vote_count":13625,"poster_path":"/4sHeTAp65WrSSuc05nRBKddhBxO.jpg","release_date":"1971-10-28","vote_average":8.18,"backdrop_path":"/nLFxvLokHe3bQmrmAfljIfax2jQ.jpg","original_title":"A Clockwork Orange","original_language":"en"},{"id":232,"adult":false,"title":"Rumble Fish","video":false,"overview":"Absent-minded street thug Rusty James struggles to live up to his legendary older brother's reputation, and longs for the days of gang warfare.","genre_ids":[80,18,10749],"popularity":3.2742,"vote_count":745,"poster_path":"/nwIUWs7cexC8Wk9c6ey8nFltAZd.jpg","release_date":"1983-10-09","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/g2SvOk7ZEgV1VyOfJB2CwFyqgmF.jpg","original_title":"Rumble Fish","original_language":"en"},{"id":479781,"adult":false,"title":"Unicorn","video":false,"overview":"A young girl of 13 lives with her mother on an isolated property. They are awaiting the return of their father and husband. But instead, another man appears, transforming the relationship between the mother and daughter. Based on two short stories by Brazilian poet Hilda Hilst.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2001,"vote_count":16,"poster_path":"/cf9JhVxOpDcPvtjnu9GNexPRwx9.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-06","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/yKuTgZeXDqDCOmVF2aBpSz26nhH.jpg","original_title":"Unicórnio","original_language":"pt"},{"id":667177,"adult":false,"title":"Dead Earth","video":false,"overview":"Two young women's plans to try to live a normal life in isolation after a world ending apocalypse go awry when they are discovered.","genre_ids":[28,18,27,53],"popularity":0.5555,"vote_count":24,"poster_path":"/dTEY7mDBVwYnByLJaJKcC4areCG.jpg","release_date":"2020-01-28","vote_average":3.333,"backdrop_path":"/jF3gk9a4t8JH0MaCCVxkXldKVDJ.jpg","original_title":"Dead Earth","original_language":"en"},{"id":14164,"adult":false,"title":"Dragonball Evolution","video":false,"overview":"On his 18th birthday, Goku receives a mystical Dragonball as a gift from his grandfather. There are only six others like it in the whole world, and legend has it that whoever possesses all seven will be granted one perfect wish. When the arrival of a dark force triggers a tragedy, Goku and his companions are propelled into an epic quest to collect the seven Dragonballs and save the Earth from destruction.","genre_ids":[28,12,14,878,53],"popularity":3.0309,"vote_count":2169,"poster_path":"/sunS9xhPnFNP5wlOWrvbpBteAB.jpg","release_date":"2009-03-12","vote_average":2.936,"backdrop_path":"/19ChHftp06sllxdgINPSTDIyKHw.jpg","original_title":"Dragonball Evolution","original_language":"en"},{"id":9504,"adult":false,"title":"Glengarry Glen Ross","video":false,"overview":"Times are tough at Premiere Properties. Shelley \"the machine\" Levene and Dave Moss are veteran salesmen, but only Ricky Roma is on a hot streak. The new Glengarry sales leads could turn everything around, but the front office is holding them back until these \"losers\" prove themselves. Then someone decides to take matters into his own hands, stealing the Glengarry leads and leaving everyone wondering who did it.","genre_ids":[80,18,9648],"popularity":2.0049,"vote_count":1554,"poster_path":"/zcaEDx8KlVfh4vKfMNLhiSi5Oz4.jpg","release_date":"1992-09-10","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/qukaw3P4MOFNdxjhNpClhT9unr8.jpg","original_title":"Glengarry Glen Ross","original_language":"en"},{"id":1463298,"adult":false,"title":"Vengeance in the Dreary Night","video":false,"overview":"Jefri and Sarah are an adulterous couple now desperately trying to create an alibi after the corpse of Sofia, the lawful wife they murdered, mysteriously disappears from the morgue. Arya Pradana, a police investigator, uses all his logic to uncover the truth. Has the corpse come back to life to take revenge on her killers?","genre_ids":[80,18,9648,53],"popularity":0.4834,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/eichIZLd7e9AgYltckEwWgrFQcq.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-28","vote_average":7.25,"backdrop_path":"/p1V67T5vf7HD91BVe4K9TUZHtl4.jpg","original_title":"Dendam Malam Kelam","original_language":"id"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt34996428","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q135726447","instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148547,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":1,"iso_639_1":"es","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-08-12T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""},{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"es","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-08-14T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""},{"note":"Disney+","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-01-16T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":["Inappropriate Language","Nudity","Violence"],"release_date":"2025-11-20T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"14"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CL","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-08-14T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"14"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CO","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-10-23T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","release_dates":[{"note":"Rome Film Fest","type":1,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-10-25T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"PE","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-09-18T00:00:00.000Z","certificati